downloadTitle: SharePoint Server 2010 Administrators and Owners Worksheet
downloadDescription: Use this worksheet to record owners for servers, sites and site collections, shared services, and central administration.
detailsSection: Use this worksheet to record owners for servers, sites and site collections, shared services, and central administration in your SharePoint Server 2010 environment.

installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button above to start the download.
